  "summary": "Mattermost doesn't validate decompressed archive entry sizes during file extraction",
  "details": "Mattermost versions 11.4.x <= 11.4.0, 11.3.x <= 11.3.1, 11.2.x <= 11.2.3, 10.11.x <= 10.11.11 fail to validate decompressed archive entry sizes during file extraction which allows authenticated users with file upload permissions to cause a denial of service via crafted zip archives containing highly compressed entries (zip bombs) that exhaust server memory. Mattermost Advisory ID: MMSA-2026-00598.",
